Module org.cojen.maker
Package org.cojen.maker

Interface Field

All Superinterfaces:
Variable
public interface Field
extends Variable
Represents a field accessible by the body of a method.
See Also:

    • set

      Field set​(Object value)
      Assign a value to this variable, either from another variable or from a constant. A constant value can be a primitive type (boxed or unboxed), null, a String, a Class, an Enum, a MethodType, or a MethodHandleInfo. Note that a MethodHandle can be set with a MethodHandleInfo, which is converted automatically at link time.
      Specified by:
      set in interface Variable
      Parameters:
      value - a Variable or a constant
      Returns:
      this variable
